snippet.title: Next Up Hero Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Next Up Hero is now available on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/667810/Next_Up_Hero/

We're excited to announce the launch of Next Up Hero, now available on Steam in Early Access, and Nintendo Switch, XboxOne and PlayStation 4 in Spring 2018! 

Learn more at NextUpHero.com!
